{"tid":1585904,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"仝人一致表揚手足以武制暴、為民除害","createTime":"2019-09-21T17:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T18:06:43.000Z","uid":148,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d29d705bb11b4145de1b544143177d9658438b18","tid":1585904,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:50:21.000Z","msg":"風向撚、有班咩都要畫面嘅阻膠麻煩你地收皮<br />\n我地有手足俾黑社會斬到殘廢<br />\n又唔見你去同黑社會講唔好斬到人殘廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地要同畜牲講道德就自己去前線講<br />\n麻煩大家熟讀牛缺者 牛缺有咩下埸就係你地班阻膠嘅下場,CE考過㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪再屈手足變怪物、咩鏡頭唔好睇、變成同佢地一樣嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對家係黑社會、黑警、藍絲<br />\n而家係打緊杖 唔係拍戲<br />\n乜撚野要鏡頭好睇,根本就係偽善嘅仆街<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再叫咩私了 係以武制暴、正當嘅自衛<br />\n我地手足打黑社會、黑警,核彈都唔會割<br />\n又唔見你地屌蝙蝠俠好暴力 <br />\n手足呢啲係俠義風骨、真英雄 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個再屌手足自衛打黑社會/藍絲<br />\n麻煩save低呢張圖提醒自己、重讀一次牛缺得到咩下場<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce31a63c867f092f3a9f29081168e8ab4edfc88","tid":1585904,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd6cbd7c1a0cc8d98ec30d8a5087606e440a168","tid":1585904,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e50ddee7593b367428c29866f0f1cf5ac06a48","tid":1585904,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"你地班道德撚同我重讀一次牛缺者 <br />\nCE考過㗎屌你老母<br />\n咁都唔明就死返去重讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>牛缺者，上地之大儒也，下之邯鄲，遇盜於耦沙之中，盡取其衣裝車，牛步而去。視之，歡然无憂𠫤之色。盜追而問其故。曰：「君子不以所養害其所養。」盜曰：「嘻！賢矣夫！」既而相謂曰：「以彼之賢，往見趙君。便以我為，必困我。不如殺之。」乃相與追而殺之。燕人聞之，聚族相戒，曰：「遇盜莫如上地之牛缺也！」皆受教。俄而其弟適秦，至闕下，果遇盜。憶其兄之戒，因與盜力爭；既而不如，又追而以卑辭請物。盜怒曰：「吾活汝弘矣，而追吾不已，迹將箸焉。既為盜矣，仁將焉在？」遂殺之，又傍害其黨四五人焉。</strong>"},{"pid":"db0790c2b4448a23330995c013be22d06d038882","tid":1585904,"uid":197103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:58:13.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n你地冇做錯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一定要防止荃灣刀手斬腳再現!</span>"},{"pid":"59cd3c12a9ef263756fab66538161e20ad70ad21","tid":1585904,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:58:17.000Z","msg":"果兩隻支那狗仆到咁，睇黎都要人道毀滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a3ce101b2a0b5332b542518d4ec9a066daadd8","tid":1585904,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"勇武手足<br />\n多謝你地,我愛你!!!!!<br />\n我愛勇武!!!!我愛勇武!!!!!"},{"pid":"bc3632868e12d52d7dc90750fa72a33bd1c53fc5","tid":1585904,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb597698bb9317e3ec5ca125b655017d18f0c999","tid":1585904,"uid":241566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6d7ff480cd281caa99c8fe949914f05dde79e0","tid":1585904,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-